                    <p>Since founding iSN.BiZ Inc in 2015, Jonathan has steered the company through transformative growth in the enterprise software landscape. His forward-thinking approach combines deep technical expertise with strategic business acumen, positioning iSN.BiZ as a trusted partner for organizations seeking to leverage cutting-edge technology for competitive advantage.</p>
                    <p>Under Jonathan's leadership, iSN.BiZ has maintained a perfect client retention rate while expanding its service offerings from traditional software development to encompass AI-powered applications, cloud-native solutions, and advanced data analytics. His ability to anticipate market trends and position the company ahead of technological shifts has been instrumental in the company's sustained success.</p>
