                    <p>Jonathan's technical foundation spans the full spectrum of modern software development. He has hands-on experience architecting scalable cloud infrastructure, implementing machine learning models, and designing enterprise-grade systems that handle millions of transactions. This technical depth enables him to guide development teams effectively while maintaining the strategic oversight necessary for executive leadership.</p>
                    <p>His expertise in AI and machine learning has been particularly valuable as the industry undergoes rapid transformation. Jonathan has pioneered the integration of large language models and generative AI into practical business applications, helping clients unlock new efficiencies and capabilities that weren't possible just a few years ago.</p>
                </div>
