                    <p>Jonathan is also passionate about fostering the next generation of technology leaders. He actively mentors his team, encouraging innovation and professional growth. This investment in people, combined with his strategic vision and technical expertise, positions iSN.BiZ for continued success in an ever-evolving technology landscape.</p>
