                    <p>His leadership style balances strategic thinking with tactical execution. Jonathan remains involved in key technical decisions while empowering his leadership team to drive their respective areas. This approach has created an agile organization that can respond quickly to market opportunities while maintaining the consistency and quality that clients expect.</p>
